channel_description: Celebrate 25 seasons of Pokémon the Series with a marathon featuring one episode from every season.

media.description: Meet Ash Ketchum, a 10-year-old boy full of imagination, confidence, and dreams that are almost too big for his village of Pallet Town—plus the desire to become a Pokémon Master!
media.title: Pokémon - I Choose You!

media.description: Ash, Tracey and Misty are sailing along on Lapras when they almost crash into another Pokémon trainer wanting to battle Ash.
media.title: Charizard Chills

media.description: When Ash hears of the nearby Charicific Valley, he is sure a quick trip would be just the thing to reignite his Charizard's flagging spirits.
media.title: Charizard's Burning Ambition

media.description: On their quest to capture Articuno on film, Todd and our heroes run into a frozen Jigglypuff!
media.title: Freeze Frame

media.description: When Ash, Misty, and Brock run to investigate a mysterious chorus of bells that spontaneously ring out, they chance to meet their old friend Morty and a Pokémon researcher of his acquaintance.
media.title: For Ho-Oh the Bells Toll

media.description: Our heroes are headed for Rustboro City, where Ash hopes to have his first real gym battle in Hoenn.
media.title: A Poached Ego

media.description: As Ash and friends walk to Lilycove City, a tree comes crashing down in front of them—pushed over by Team Rocket in their newest giant robot!
media.title: A Scare to Remember

media.description: Max and May come to visit Ash in Pallet Town, along with Misty and Brock, and they all make plans for another journey together—this time, to the Battle Frontier!
media.title: The Right Place and the Right Mime

media.description: Ash has arrived at Metallica Island, home of the Battle Palace. He's ready for battle, but Sceptile isn't—its attack moves still aren't working and it runs away in frustration.
media.title: Cutting the Ties That Bind

media.description: When Ash and his friends pass a village that's holding an informal Pokémon Contest where the prize is a year's supply of fruit, Dawn is eager to enter.
media.title: Borrowing on Bad Faith

media.description: While Ash's Pokémon train for the upcoming Pastoria Gym battle, Gligar is blown away by a sudden gust of wind. Gligar lands on Team Rocket's balloon—accidentally ripping a hole in it with its claws.
media.title: Chim-Charred

media.description: As our heroes travel through the forest, Dawn stops at a spring by a river to refill her water bottle. A wild Aggron suddenly attacks her, and she falls into the river.
media.title: Trials and Adulations!

media.description: When Ash arrives at the Sunyshore Gym for his next Gym battle, its uninspired Gym Leader refuses to accept his challenge!
media.title: Flint Sparks the Fire!

media.description: Many of our heroes’ Pokémon have fallen ill from the poison spores of a group of Foongus, and Oshawott must face its fear to help provide the cure!
media.title: Facing Fear with Eyes Wide Open!

media.description: An encounter with Pikachu’s old rival puts our heroes in the middle of a bullying confrontation!
media.title: Battling the Bully!

media.description: After discovering a festival celebrating the sights and sounds of the Kanto region, Ash reunites with an old friend who shows what real staying power is all about!
media.title: The Fires of a Red-Hot Reunion!

media.description: Clemont revisits his school days and meets up with a few old friends, both people and Pokémon!
media.title: A Campus Reunion!

media.description: A conflict of heartfelt emotions threatens the future of a longstanding partnership!
media.title: A Fork in the Road! A Parting of the Ways!

media.description: Following Ash’s defeat at the Snowbelle Gym, some not-so-quiet introspection turns into some real inspiration!
media.title: Seeing the Forest for the Trees!

media.description: The ending of one chapter in the life of a determined Pokémon ushers in the beginning of a brand-new one!
media.title: One Journey Ends, Another Begins...

media.description: Professors Kukui and Burnet are getting married, and our heroes know just what to do to help!
media.title: The Professors’ New Adventure!

media.description: With their big vacation on the horizon, our heroes are setting some life-changing plans into motion!
media.title: Thank You, Alola! The Journey Continues!

media.description: As Ash and Goh explore a distant island in search of Mew, their research takes an unexpected, powerful turn!
media.title: Getting More Than You Battled For!

media.description: An unexpected Evolution brings back an unexpected memory for Goh!
media.title: Not Too Close for Comfort!

media.description: There’s an unintended change of plans as Ash winds up watching some training that’s like nothing he’s ever seen!
media.title: Meeting Up With the Monarch!
